 input in choosing his own team in part because he wants people to compensate for his own inexperience in dealing with congress other white house aides said that was a polite way of saying that mr panettas two deputies harold m ickes and evelyn lieberman would almost certainly not stay onas codeputy chief of staff with mr bowles under mr panetta mr ickes served as political strategist and ambassador to democratic constituency groups while mr bowles oversaw internal administration and the presidents time the two made a good team but have little in common advertisement continue reading the main story mr bowles is no stranger to politics he comes from a prominent north carolina family and his late father hargrove bowles was the democratic candidate for governor of north carolina in  his wife crandall close bowles is the sister of elliot s close who lost his challenge to senator strom thurmond of south carolina this week newsletter sign up continue reading the main story please verify youre not a robot by clicking the box invalid email address please reenter you must select a newsletter to subscribe to sign up you agree to receive occasional updates and special offers for the new york timess products and services thank you for subscribing an error has occurred please try again later you are already subscribed to this email view all new york times newsletters see sample manage email preferences not you privacy policy opt out or contact us anytime the closes are descendants of the family that founded springs industries the south carolina textile giant that makes springmaid and wamsutta sheets and mrs bowles is the companys executive vice president and head of its bath division and a candidate for the top job one day company records show that she is a millionaire many times over she was a wellesley college classmate of hillary rodham clintonsmr bowles who graduated from the university of north carolina and holds an mba from columbia university met crandall close when they 